name: GetLeaseDetails
description:
Retrieve detailed information about leases.

Use this tool to get detailed information about leases, including lease activities, details, documents, parcels, and more. It supports pagination for handling large datasets.

parameters.name: client_subdomain
parameters.description: The subdomain representing the client organization. Required to specify which client's data to retrieve.

parameters.name: lease_documents_upload
parameters.description: Upload lease documents using a form file upload (multipart/form-data).

value_schema.description:
## Note: 
 **sendLeaseDocuments** API accepts files as a form file upload, Please select the option `multipart/form-data` from the Request body dropdown to see further details.
 To test the sendLeaseDocuments API or see the additional details, please click the `Try it out` button.

parameters.name: page_number
parameters.description: The page number to retrieve in a paginated response. Use this to navigate through pages of lease details.

value_schema.description: The page number of paginated respons.

parameters.name: items_per_page
parameters.description: The number of items to return per page in the response. Supports paginated data retrieval.

value_schema.description: The number of items returned in the respnose

parameters.name: include_pagination_links
parameters.description: Set to 1 to include pagination links in the response. Use 0 to exclude them. This helps manage paginated data effectively.

value_schema.description: Send Pagination Links in Response Body.
